metadata.name: PRESENCE OF A LEADER
metadata.description:
𝕻𝖗𝖊𝖘𝖊𝖓𝖙𝖎𝖆 𝕯𝖚𝖈𝖎𝖘 (𝐎𝐒𝐌𝐎𝐒𝐈𝐒®)  
Made with Photoshop + AI  
4000 X 6000 PX  
PNG 40.9 MB  
5/5

Everything I've endured has amounted to something greater. All of my frustrations and failures have brought me to a place of understanding, and I'm learning to embrace the present and the lessons that it teaches me. As the saying goes, 'When the student is ready, the teacher will appear'. Those that have been present in my past, in my dreams, and in my heart are the people that are here now. I see them everywhere, in the most unlikely of places. I see the sweetest smiles, the most innocent of laughs, and a peace that surpasses all understanding. I know that I'm chosen, that I'm here for a reason, and that I have a purpose. I will accomplish everything that I'm destined to do, and that is a promise.
